recommended_for_you.title: Recommended
recommended_for_you.description: We picked these out just for you.

389496.title: What's the Worst That Could Happen?
389496.description: A professional thief tries to rob a billionaire's mansion. But when the crook’s lucky ring is stolen, he vows revenge in this laugh-out-loud comedy.

476915.title: Detachment
476915.description: A substitute teacher who shuns emotional connection bonds with a runaway teenager and becomes a role model for apathetic students at a public school.

477962.title: Set It Off
477962.description: Four African-American women in Los Angeles, all in dire financial circumstances, resort to robbing banks with action-packed, tragic consequences.

494842.title: Shottas
494842.description: Two young men from Jamaica climb to the top of the criminal world in Miami, with a constant presence of drugs, extortion, and deceit.

528667.title: When the Bough Breaks
528667.description: The trust between a married couple and the woman carrying their child is torn when the surrogate decides she wants the husband and baby for herself.

545561.title: Orphan
545561.description: A couple mourning the loss of their unborn baby adopt a little girl, except her new mom suspects something is disturbingly wrong with the child.

554502.title: Brooklyn's Finest
554502.description: Throughout one week, the lives of three very different New York City police officers change as a result of a violent drug operation.

554542.title: School Dance
554542.description: Being a high school freshman is no walk in the park, but it’s even tougher as a teenager finds his dream girl and she has no idea he even exists.

557519.title: After Earth
557519.description: Following a crash landing on Earth, a young boy and his estranged father must make an arduous journey and survive the elements to signal for help.

559020.title: Terrifier
559020.description: A maniacal clown uses gruesome methods to viciously torture and murder women who have the unfortunate luck of entering his house of horrors.

563038.title: Deuce Bigalow: Male Gigolo
563038.description: A professional fish tank cleaner in desperate need of cash turns to the world's oldest profession and becomes a lover for hire.

589161.title: Class Act
589161.description: When a bookworm and a juvenile delinquent find their academic records switched on the first day of school, they use the mix-up to their advantage.

589177.title: Money Talks
589177.description: A con man, in need of protection from the cops, the mob, and his pregnant girlfriend, joins forces with a struggling TV newsman in need of a story.

610961.title: High Crimes
610961.description: When a savvy lawyer learns her husband is roped into a possible government conspiracy, she gets help in her investigation from a veteran military attorney.

610966.title: The League of Extraordinary Gentlemen
610966.description: A team of fantastical superheroes from literary tales are assembled by a notorious adventurer in order to save the planet from annihilation.

619660.title: Ip Man 3 (English Dub)
619660.description: Hong Kong, 1959. A crooked real estate developer leads a band of gangsters in a property coup that can only be stopped by the Wing Chun grandmaster.

621292.title: Black Dog
621292.description: An ex-convict truck driver with makes one last no-questions-asked trip, only to discover that his rig is stocked with assault weapons.

621746.title: Stomp the Yard
621746.description: Amazing step dancing sequences spice up this story of a college freshman with a past trying to fit in while joining a rival fraternity out to win.

642254.title: The Girl with All the Gifts
642254.description: In a bleak future, mankind has succumbed to a fungus that turns everyone into flesh-eating monsters, until an immune child is discovered.

654077.title: Leap!
654077.description: An ambitious orphan with dreams of becoming a ballerina makes her way to the Paris Opera where she auditions for the lead in "The Nutcracker.”

657079.title: Let's Go to Prison
657079.description: When Fate steers a career criminal’s plot for revenge off-course, he sends his intended victim’s kid to prison, and then joins him in the slammer.

658066.title: Riding in Cars With Boys
658066.description: Set in 1965, a 15-year-old girl with dreams of becoming a writer gets pregnant and enters a failed marriage with the baby’s drug-addicted father.

672234.title: Meet the Blacks
672234.description: After Carl Black moves his family to Beverly Hills, their arrival is timed with the city's annual purge, where all crime is legal for 12 hours.

694396.title: It
694396.description: In the town of Derry, Maine, seven young kids band together to stop a new killing cycle of an ancient, shape-shifting predator they can only call It.

708829.title: The Stepmother 2
708829.description: Elizabeth breaks free from the hospital with a new mission - find a new family and live happily ever after, she can’t escape her past and will fight.

712894.title: The Help
712894.description: In 1960s Mississippi, a Southern girl turns her small town on its ear when she interviews African-American maids who have worked for white families.

713530.title: The Corrupted
713530.description: An ex-con trying to live a peaceful life is thrust into action and must risk it all when his brother gets entangled in a dangerous web of corruption.

713911.title: Homewrecker
713911.description: A married couple decides to rent out the extra room in their house to an attractive young woman who moves in armed with a set of filthy schemes.

716389.title: Poltergeist
716389.description: In this reimagining of the 1982 classic, a family fights to rescue their daughter from a demon invading their home through a portal to another world.

724344.title: You're Not Alone
724344.description: 30,000 ft in the air, Keith Mitchell (Michael Jai White) helplessly watches a stranger enter his home. There’s only one problem; his daughter is there.

724735.title: True to the Game 3
724735.description: Gena wakes to find Quadir is her savior and has just 72 hrs to return to Philly to let Bria and Gah Git know her plans, before her happily ever after.

100000194.title: I Got the Hook-Up 2
100000194.description: After a health inspector threatens to shut down a restaurant, young hustlers Fatboy and Spyda attempt to pull off a scam to save it from closure.

100000221.title: Smurfs: The Lost Village
100000221.description: A mysterious map sends the Smurfs on a thrilling race through a forbidden forest filled with magical creatures to find a forgotten hamlet.

100000379.title: Classmates
100000379.description: A computer mixup gives two college freshman the chance to swap places but things take a turn when the switch puts them both in danger.

100000849.title: All Eyez on Me
100000849.description: This biopic chronicles the ascent of hip-hop legend and activist Tupac Shakur centering on the relationships and experiences that shaped his artistry.

100001591.title: Space Jam: A New Legacy
100001591.description: When a rogue artificial intelligence kidnaps his son, LeBron James recruits the Looney Tunes to face off against the Goons in a game of basketball.

100001592.title: Tom & Jerry: The Movie
100001592.description: A desperate event planner conspires with Tom to catch his nemesis Jerry as the mouse wreaks havoc throughout a fancy Manhattan hotel during a wedding.

100001594.title: Rampage
100001594.description: When a group of animals becomes vicious after a genetic experiment goes awry, a primatologist must find an antidote to avert a global catastrophe.

100001596.title: Mortal Kombat
100001596.description: An MMA fighter with a mysterious dragon birthmark learns that he’s been chosen to fight for Earthrealm in the final battle against the evil Outworld.

100001597.title: It: Chapter Two
100001597.description: When Pennywise resurfaces after 27 years, the Losers Club reunites to prevent another reign of terror and defeat It once and for all.

100001652.title: Quik Money
100001652.description: After a close brush with the law, a hustler reinvents himself as a tax guru and finds himself reaping big rewards and taking on bigger risks.

100001703.title: Tyler Perry's Acrimony
100001703.description: A faithful wife tired of standing by her devious husband is enraged when it becomes clear she has been betrayed by him financially.

100001741.title: Nerve
100001741.description: A high school senior finds herself immersed in an online game of truth or dare, where her every move becomes manipulated by a community of "watchers."

100002155.title: A Body to Kill For
100002155.description: Growing up in Philadelphia, China enjoys a life of privilege until a handsome suitor exposes her to a dark side of the city that changes her forever.

100002158.title: Grown Ups
100002158.description: Five high school buddies reunite after 30 years to mourn the loss of their basketball coach and wrestle with the challenges of adulthood.

100002306.title: Behind the Veil
100002306.description: To the community, Stacey and Darrel are models of hope, success and strength. But behind closed doors, addiction and betrayal are ripping them apart.

100002566.title: Watch Your Back
100002566.description: As one of Detroit's top strippers, Kanisha effortlessly seduces and manipulates men out of their money to fund her extravagant lifestyle.

04430.title: Haven
04430.description: Crime series with supernatural shadings as an FBI agent assigned to a case in Maine finds herself on the trail of unexplained and spooky occurrences.

04294.title: Dance Moms
04294.description: Popular reality series following the tough love teaching by a dance instructor-choreographer of talented tweens and her occasional parental run-ins.

0300008167.title: Bad Girls Club
0300008167.description: A group of women with anger and control issues come together and try to improve themselves. But moving forward isn’t going to be easy.

01627.title: Hunter X Hunter (English Subtitle)
01627.description: A young boy, who dreams of being a hunter like his father, must pass the notoriously difficult and dangerous Hunter Qualification Exam.

02348.title: Duck Dynasty
02348.description: Follow the Robertsons as they run a multi-million dollar sporting empire and face everything from beavers to business deals, in this reality series.

0300000080.title: The Book of Negroes
0300000080.description: Kidnapped in Africa and enslaved in South Carolina as a girl, a woman attempts to secure her freedom in eighteenth century North America.

0300010082.title: Third Watch
0300010082.description: A drama about the brave and dedicated people who serve as paramedics, firefighters, and police on the “third watch,” the 3:00 PM to 11:00 PM shift.

0300008457.title: The Jeffersons
0300008457.description: Class, race, neighbors, family, and all kinds of clashes make for classic comedy in this beloved series about a family’s move on up to luxury living.

0300008639.title: The Steve Harvey Show
0300008639.description: Steve Harvey's sitcom from the WB network is classic '90s comedy about a musician-turned-teacher who teaches his unruly students a thing or three!

0300000124.title: Gilligan's Island
0300000124.description: Shipwrecked on an uncharted South Pacific island, seven castaways struggle to survive the outdoors—and each other—in this wacky classic comedy series.

0300009902.title: Southland
0300009902.description: When a seasoned cop is assigned to train a rookie, his no-nonsense approach makes the young man question if he has what it takes to become an officer.

0300006058.title: The Client List
0300006058.description: Jennifer Love Hewitt stars as Riley, a newly single mother who accepts employment at a day spa which offers some scandalous services.

0300010390.title: Extreme Cheapskates
0300010390.description: Spotlighting frugalists who will do anything to save a penny, this series explores the extreme lengths people will go to cut costs in their lives.

04893.title: McGraw Avenue
04893.description: In a notorious Detroit neighborhood, two men with different goals navigate the streets and deal with complex characters, to both survive and dominate.

0300009246.title: Line of Duty
0300009246.description: Under the supervision of Superintendent Ted Hastings, British detectives in anti-corruption police unit AC-12 investigate suspected dirty cops.

0300010244.title: Miami Vice
0300010244.description: From executive producer Michael Mann comes the explosive, groundbreaking detective show that redefined the word "cool” in the mid-1980s.

0300010053.title: Fantasy Island (2021 Series)
0300010053.description: This modern drama series takes place at a luxury resort, where any fantasy requested by guests is fulfilled—although they rarely turn out as expected.

0300009219.title: Quantico
0300009219.description: FBI recruits form friendships while training at Quantico Base. But relationships are tested when one of them becomes a suspect in a terrorist attack.

0300000081.title: Hell on Wheels
0300000081.description: An epic story of post-Civil War America, focusing on a Confederate soldier who sets out to exact revenge on the Union soldiers who killed his wife.

0300008306.title: Next Level Chef
0300008306.description: Celebrity chef Gordon Ramsay hosts ambitious chefs facing unique cooking challenges, in a culinary competition to be the food world’s next superstar.

0300006728.title: Columbo
0300006728.description: This beloved series features the brilliant bumbling detective who despite his easygoing nature, always manages to crack the case.

0300008079.title: The Bernie Mac Show
0300008079.description: Bernie Mac stars as a stand up comic who, alongside his businesswoman wife, must take in his sister's three kids while she's in rehab.

0300006821.title: Ambitions
0300006821.description: Two top Atlanta lawyers compete in personal and professional endeavors, in a battle of ambitions that so often gets out of control.

02914.title: Forensic Files
02914.description: Witnesses, investigators and medical experts lend their unique perspective on true crime in every episode of this long-running docuseries.

03697.title: V
03697.description: When human-looking aliens known as Visitors appear in every major city U.S. promoting peace, an FBI counter-terrorist discovers their deadly plot.

0300007917.title: Secrets and Lies
0300007917.description: Juliette Lewis stars as a determined and brilliant detective whose latest murder case challenges her and her team with a family’s secrets and lies.

0300000159.title: Hannibal
0300000159.description: An FBI investigator with the ability to empathize with psychopaths is assigned to work with renowned psychiatrist—and secret cannibal—Hannibal Lecter.

0300009178.title: The Dirty D
0300009178.description: In Detroit's hottest nightclub, there are no rules, nothing is off-limits, and everyone plays for keeps! It's a dirty game! Welcome to the Dirty D!

0300010238.title: Bad Girls All-Star Battle
0300010238.description: Bad Girls All-Star Battle features fun, over-the-top physical and mental challenges that will test the limits of the world's feistiest ladies.

03320.title: Hell's Kitchen
03320.description: Renowned restauranteur Gordon Ramsay hosts a fierce competition for aspiring chefs, as they vie for a prestigious job at one of his eateries.

0300006854.title: Scooby-Doo Where Are You?
0300006854.description: The classic adventures of the lovable Great Dane and his human companions as they hunt for clues, hungry for a solution to mysteries and a snack.

0300009281.title: Everybody Hates Chris
0300009281.description: Comedian Chris Rock narrates the hilarious, touching story of a teenager growing up as the eldest of three children in Brooklyn during the 1980s.

0300010281.title: Breaking Amish
0300010281.description: Follow young adults from the Amish and Mennonite communities as they leave their homes to experiment with "new world" freedoms in New York City.

0300006059.title: Kevin Can Wait
0300006059.description: A newly retired police officer has to reconsider his plans when his daughter announces she’s dropping out of college to support her fiancé.

04631.title: Degrassi: The Next Generation
04631.description: Long-running TV-series, acclaimed for its powerful realism in taking on the life-changing issues facing a group of friends at a Toronto high school.

03646.title: Little Women: Atlanta
03646.description: There's no shortage of excitement in this circle of friends as they face the daily challenges that come with being a little person in the big city.

0300007764.title: Pokémon the Series: Black & White
0300007764.description: Ash and Pikachu are off to the distant Unova region, where they'll encounter new friends, new rivals, new challenges, and all-new Pokémon! Upon arrival, Ash meets aspiring Dragon Master Iris, full of spirit and determination, and Pokémon Connoisseur Cilan, who is always available to lend his expertise. Above all, Ash will need plenty of new Pokémon on his team if he wants to win Unova's tournaments and Gym badges. Following his every move is the criminal trio of Team Rocket, with sinister new schemes and a fresh resolve to catch Pikachu! Then there's the mysterious N...is he a friend or a foe, and what is his connection with the secret organization known as Team Plasma? And what is Team Plasma planning to do with one of the Legendary Pokémon of the Unova region? Once this adventure starts, the excitement won't stop!
